data.description: Opportunity Knocks! This Centrally located home is ready for its new owners to bring it into the 21st century. Built in 1955 this home features 3 cozy bedrooms and an updated bath with a large walk in shower. You'll have plenty of natural light in the main living areas with the large front window and sliding glass doors. Spend your evenings relaxing in your partially enclosed and covered back patio looking over the low maintenance desert scaped yard.. Are you concerned about big ticket repairs in an older home? Have peace of mind knowing your new homes AC was replaced in 2019 as well as new sewer lines in 2018. Just minutes from downtown, Shopping and Restaurants!
